<p>Pixi seems like a really nice environment manager. I especially like that you can run things from outside the env. Thereâs benefits to having the environment with the project, both for easier cleanup but also to easily have scripts associated with an environment. I like that conda keeps all the environments in one place, it feels clean, but this way also makes a lot of sense.</p>
</section>
